vernac_cmds: Local Notation "e [ v / x ]" := (vec_change e x v).
Inductive mm_instr n : Set := | mm_inc : pos n -> mm_instr n | mm_dec : pos n -> nat -> mm_instr n .

Inductive mm_sss : mm_instr n -> mm_state -> mm_state -> Prop := | in_mm_sss_inc : forall i x v, INC x // (i,v) -1> (1+i,v[(S (v#>x))/x]) | in_mm_sss_dec_0 : forall i x k v, v#>x = O -> DEC x k // (i,v) -1> (k,v) | in_mm_sss_dec_1 : forall i x k v u, v#>x = S u -> DEC x k // (i,v) -1> (1+i,v[u/x]) where "i // s -1> t" := (mm_sss i s t).
Fact mm_sss_fun i s t1 t2 : i // s -1> t1 -> i // s -1> t2 -> t1 = t2.
rewrite H in H6; inversion H6; subst; auto.
Fact mm_sss_total ii s : { t | ii // s -1> t }.
destruct ii as [ x | x j ]; [ | case_eq (v#>x); [ | intros k ]; intros E ].
Fact mm_sss_INC_inv x i v j w : INC x // (i,v) -1> (j,w) -> j=1+i /\ w = v[(S (v#>x))/x].
Fact mm_sss_DEC0_inv x k i v j w : v#>x = O -> DEC x k // (i,v) -1> (j,w) -> j = k /\ w = v.
intros H; inversion 1; subst; auto; rewrite H in H2; try discriminate.
Fact mm_sss_DEC1_inv x k u i v j w : v#>x = S u -> DEC x k // (i,v) -1> (j,w) -> j=1+i /\ w = v[u/x].
intros H; inversion 1; subst; auto; rewrite H in H2; try discriminate.
Notation "P // s -[ k ]-> t" := (sss_steps mm_sss P k s t).
Notation "P // s -+> t" := (sss_progress mm_sss P s t).
Notation "P // s ->> t" := (sss_compute mm_sss P s t).
Fact mm_progress_INC P i x v st : (i,INC x::nil) <sc P -> P // (1+i,v[(S (v#>x))/x]) ->> st -> P // (i,v) -+> st.
Corollary mm_compute_INC P i x v st : (i,INC x::nil) <sc P -> P // (1+i,v[(S (v#>x))/x]) ->> st -> P // (i,v) ->> st.
intros; apply sss_progress_compute; eapply mm_progress_INC; eauto.
Fact mm_progress_DEC_0 P i x k v st : (i,DEC x k::nil) <sc P -> v#>x = O -> P // (k,v) ->> st -> P // (i,v) -+> st.
Corollary mm_compute_DEC_0 P i x k v st : (i,DEC x k::nil) <sc P -> v#>x = O -> P // (k,v) ->> st -> P // (i,v) ->> st.
intros; apply sss_progress_compute; eapply mm_progress_DEC_0; eauto.
Fact mm_progress_DEC_S P i x k v u st : (i,DEC x k::nil) <sc P -> v#>x = S u -> P // (1+i,v[u/x]) ->> st -> P // (i,v) -+> st.
Corollary mm_compute_DEC_S P i x k v u st : (i,DEC x k::nil) <sc P -> v#>x = S u -> P // (1+i,v[u/x]) ->> st -> P // (i,v) ->> st.
intros; apply sss_progress_compute; eapply mm_progress_DEC_S; eauto.
Fact mm_steps_INC_inv k P i x v st : (i,INC x::nil) <sc P -> k <> 0 -> P // (i,v) -[k]-> st -> exists k', k' < k /\ P // (1+i,v[(S (v#>x))/x]) -[k']-> st.
destruct H4 as [ (? & ?) | (k' & st2 & ? & H4 & H5) ]; subst; auto.
apply sss_step_subcode_inv with (1 := H1) in H4.
Fact mm_steps_DEC_0_inv k P i x p v st : (i,DEC x p::nil) <sc P -> k <> 0 -> v#>x = 0 -> P // (i,v) -[k]-> st -> exists k', k' < k /\ P // (p,v) -[k']-> st.
destruct H4 as [ (? & ?) | (k' & st2 & ? & H4 & H5) ]; subst; auto.
apply sss_step_subcode_inv with (1 := H1) in H4.
Fact mm_steps_DEC_1_inv k P i x p v u st : (i,DEC x p::nil) <sc P -> k <> 0 -> v#>x = S u -> P // (i,v) -[k]-> st -> exists k', k' < k /\ P // (1+i,v[u/x]) -[k']-> st.
destruct H4 as [ (? & ?) | (k' & st2 & ? & H4 & H5) ]; subst; auto.
apply sss_step_subcode_inv with (1 := H1) in H4.
inversion H4; subst; auto; rewrite H3 in H9.
Local Notation "P // s -[ k ]-> t" := (sss_steps (@mm_sss _) P k s t).
Local Notation "P // s -+> t" := (sss_progress (@mm_sss _) P s t).
Local Notation "P // s ->> t" := (sss_compute (@mm_sss _) P s t).
Tactic Notation "mm" "sss" "INC" "with" uconstr(a) := match goal with | |- _ // _ -+> _ => apply mm_progress_INC with (x := a) | |- _ // _ ->> _ => apply mm_compute_INC with (x := a) end; auto.

Tactic Notation "mm" "sss" "DEC" "0" "with" uconstr(a) uconstr(b) := match goal with | |- _ // _ -+> _ => apply mm_progress_DEC_0 with (x := a) (k := b) | |- _ // _ ->> _ => apply mm_compute_DEC_0 with (x := a) (k := b) end; auto.

Tactic Notation "mm" "sss" "DEC" "S" "with" uconstr(a) uconstr(b) uconstr(c) := match goal with | |- _ // _ -+> _ => apply mm_progress_DEC_S with (x := a) (k := b) (u := c) | |- _ // _ ->> _ => apply mm_compute_DEC_S with (x := a) (k := b) (u := c) end; auto.
Tactic Notation "mm" "sss" "stop" := exists 0; apply sss_steps_0; auto.
Definition MM_PROBLEM := { n : nat & { P : list (mm_instr n) & vec nat n } }.
Local Notation "i // s -1> t" := (@mm_sss _ i s t).
Local Notation "P // s ~~> t" := (sss_output (@mm_sss _) P s t).
Definition MM_HALTS_ON_ZERO (P : MM_PROBLEM) := match P with existT _ n (existT _ P v) => (1,P) // (1,v) ~~> (0,vec_zero) end.
Definition MM_HALTING (P : MM_PROBLEM) := match P with existT _ n (existT _ P v) => (1, P) // (1, v) ↓ end.
Variables (n : nat) (P : nat*list (mm_instr n)) (se : nat * vec nat n) (Q : nat * vec nat n -> Prop).
Hypothesis (HQ0 : Q se) (HQ1 : forall i ρ v j w, (i,ρ::nil) <sc P -> ρ // (i,v) -1> (j,w) -> P // (j,w) ->> se -> Q (j,w) -> Q (i,v)).
Theorem mm_special_ind s : P // s ->> se -> Q s.
induction q as [ | q IHq ]; intros s Hs.
apply sss_steps_0_inv in Hs; subst; apply HQ0.
destruct Hs as ((j,w) & (j' & l & ρ & r & u & G1 & G2 & G3) & Hs2); subst s P.
apply HQ1 with (i := j'+length l) (2 := G3); auto.
Variables (n : nat) (P : nat*list (mm_instr n)) (se : nat * vec nat n) (Q : nat * vec nat n -> Prop).
Hypothesis (HQ0 : out_code (fst se) P -> Q se) (HQ1 : forall i ρ v j w, (i,ρ::nil) <sc P -> ρ // (i,v) -1> (j,w) -> P // (j,w) ~~> se -> Q (j,w) -> Q (i,v)).
Theorem mm_term_ind s : P // s ~~> se -> Q s.
revert s H1; apply mm_special_ind; auto.
intros i rho v j w' H1 H3 H4.
